{
  "name": "RPlog_Avid_and_Sinjon_Torment_Morganna",
  "title": "Avid and Sinjon Torment Morganna",
  "summary": "In the KOS Gardens of a Caspian station, the hungover, scarred drifter Morganna emerges from sleeping under a bush and, in a cruel mood, decides to sneak up on the small-business pilot Avid. Her attempt to startle him backfires into a clumsy scuffle that lands them both tangled on the grass, aggravating Morganna's recently injured knee. The cheerful Mashi Horansi gardener Sinjon Teague comes running at the commotion and helps the pair up with good humor, then quietly probes Morganna's mind through the Force, warning that her control over her dark anger is slipping and offering a path toward the Light should she ever seek it. The bystander Alan and his yappy puppy Muffle add to the chaos. Increasingly rattled by Sinjon's mental intrusions and her swelling knee, Morganna refuses Avid's offers of help and limps off toward the medical center, while Avid returns Alan's dog and follows after her.",
